# UI — packages/ui

## Scope

- Source-export package, no build step.
- Contains shadcn primitives, `cn`, typography, Tailwind v4 styles/tokens, and cross-app UI helpers.
- Do not add app-specific shells, routing components, or data-table abstractions here unless both landing and dashboard need them.

## Imports

- Public imports: `@repo/ui` (barrel), `@repo/ui/components/button`, `@repo/ui/lib/utils`, `@repo/ui/globals.css`.
- shadcn CLI in apps routes primitives via `@repo/ui/components` aliases; within `packages/ui` aliases stay relative (`src/components`, `src/lib`).
- Internal component imports should stay relative or package-safe.

## Primitives policy

- Default headless primitives: `radix-ui` (shadcn `radix-nova` style).
- `@base-ui/react` — только для `Combobox` (нет аналога в текущем radix-наборе).
- Cross-app presentational blocks: `ai-disclaimer-text`, `route-error-fallback-content`, `route-not-found-layout`, `brand-link-label`.

## Design

- Use semantic Tailwind tokens only.
- Keep Phosphor Icons as the icon system.
- Financial values use tabular numerals.
